{"tid":492120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到有一論調好有趣：連登郁啲就話人係雞，高登唔會","createTime":"2017-12-07T08:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T08:41:51.000Z","uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65ac54670c4ad8d6f5a4f6e85b5372aaa7d64e46","tid":492120,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗想當年，就上年年頭既事<br />\nRubbishptgf首先係高登爆好多女都做雞<br />\n<br />\n跟住大家都跟住股熱潮係咁post ig雞來討論<br />\n之後高登仲有人作埋首歌：雞 全部都係雞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁試問邊個討論區郁啲就話人係雞先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都可以怪一個forum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種論調有啲似女權撚咁<br />\n<br />\n見到果邊仲係咁多人係度做<span style=\"color: red;\">言論導向</span><br />\n果邊 每個post睇落去都硬係有啲野咁<br />\n令人讀完硬係想有一種message要你接收<br />\n唔洗呢啲係咪洗腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係打手或者有人過左去玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我想無論連登定高登 最珍貴都係管理者無為而治<br />\n唔引導言論，開放平台<br />\n<br />\n係呢點上 高登似乎仲未擺脫呢個陰霾<br />\n因為高登曾經俾中共打手，商業打手佔據過大段唔短既時間<br />\n唔知呢啲打手是否林早洩引入或者默許啦<br />\n但我覺得佢始終對運用呢種手法樂之不疲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其佢本人同間公司已經染紅了啦"},{"pid":"86af17cfb9f67f84e63ccd554c77a6c608b2bc97","tid":492120,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d640635752571d3783994f96d08c97a75cbd10e","tid":492120,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩膠還玩膠<br />\n唔好推人入火坑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}